        li Spanish vs Mayan Officials
        li Education concerns
        li Wealth Difference

  .slide
    h2 Guatemalan Elections: Emotive Communication
    ul
      li Often show people of similar situations
      li Show "Power", "Protection" and Wealth
      li Bribe votes using Government programs, food giveaways and promises
      li Mexican Drug Cartels and Violence
    center
      img.framed(src='/img/election1.jpg')

    .speaker
      ul
        li Compare to American Politics
        li Many "Basic" human needs vs America's Wealth needs
        li Bought with Money/Promises
        li Drug Cartels and Violence

  .slide
    h2 What You Should Take Away
    ul
      li Perception is all around us, positive and negative<br><br>
      li Emotive Communication is one of the most common, and most powerful<br><br>
      li Be aware of your use of perception and emotive communication
        ul
          li In everyday life
          li How it's used against you.

